xbird.util.collections
Class Int2QCache<V>

java.lang.Object
  xbird.util.collections.IntHash<V>
      xbird.util.collections.Int2QCache<V>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, Externalizable, Serializable, Iterable<IntHash.BucketEntry<V>>
public class Int2QCache<V>
extends IntHash<V>

Implementation of a cache with the full two-queue page replacement policy.

Get detail on the following paper. Theodore Johnson, Dennis Shasha: 2Q: A Low Overhead High Performance Buffer Management Replacement Algorithm. In Proc. VLDB, pp.439-450, 1994.

Author:
Makoto YUI (yuin405+xbird@gmail.com)
